::Skulletron::

       Skulletron grinned.

       "I've already seen every area of the ship, but I haven't been to
them.  I have access to all of the Cybertronian Fire.  I also have knowledge
of the bot's names.  In fact, right now, I could incinerate all the Maximals
here by changing the autogun settings, if I felt like it.  But, there's no
need for anyone to die on this mission.  Here, we'll tour the ship together,
and I'll try to patch some information back to the Alliance base, for
Zardus.  Let's go," He said, as he grabbed Feline's hand and held it in his
own two hands.
